data.description: Welcome to 715 Compton Street. This cute ranch home has much more room than it looks. As you enter, you find a nice living room area with updated flooring, fresh paint and more. There is a nice dining room area and two spacious bedrooms on the first level. The bedrooms also have fresh paint and newer flooring. The kitchen features nice stainless steel appliances. The huge bonus room upstairs could be used as a playroom, office, or bedroom. As you make your way down to the lower level you will find two additional rooms that would be perfect for an office, workout room, etc. There is another full bathroom in the lower level with a standup shower. Finally, this cute home has a nice sized back yard as well as a 1 car attached garage. The central location is within minutes to the University of Louisville and the historic Churchill Downs racetrack. Property sold AS IS with absolutely no warranties expressed written or implied. Buyer to verify any and all information or lack of information including but not limited to square footage, lot size, utilities, foundations, environmental concerns, zoning and intended uses, etc.
